description: Provides pan-European CORINE Land Cover inventory for 44 thematic classes for the 2018 reference year. The dataset  has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 25 hectares (ha) for areal phenomena and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 100 m for linear phenomena and is available as vector and as 100 m raster data.
title: CORINE Land Cover 2018 (vector/raster 100 m), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides land cover change information between the 2012 and 2018 CLC status layers. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 5 hectares (ha) and is available as vector and as 100 m raster data.
title: CORINE Land Cover Change 2012-2018 (vector/raster 100 m), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides auxiliary information in the spatial resolution of 10 m on the trees in agricultural use and urban context, used for production of the Forest Type dataset for the 2018 reference year. Data is sourced from Corine Land Cover and High Resolution Layer Imperviousness.
title: Forest Additional Support Layer 2018 (raster 10 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides a pan-European spatially consistent and seamless, detailed land cover inventory for the 2018 reference year, for each polygon showing the dominant land cover among the 18 basic land cover classes and additional attributes. The minimum mapping unit of the dataset is 0.5 ha.
title: CLCplus Backbone 2018 (vector), Europe

description: Provides auxiliary information in the spatial resolution of 10 m on the trees in agricultural use and urban context, used for production of the Forest Type dataset for the 2021 reference year. Data is sourced from Corine Land Cover and High Resolution Layer Imperviousness.
title: Forest Additional Support Layer 2021 (raster 10 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides at pan-European level in the spatial resolution of 10 m a basic land cover classification with two thematic classes (herbaceous / non-herbaceous) for the 2018 reference year.
title: Herbaceous cover 2018 (raster 10 m), Europe, yearly

description: Provides detailed land cover and land use information for 55 thematic classes in selected Natura2000 sites for the 2018 reference year. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 0.5 ha and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 10 m and is available as vector data.
title: N2K Land Cover/Land Use 2018 (vector), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides a pan-European spatially consistent and seamless, detailed land cover inventory for the 2018 reference year, for each pixel showing the dominant land cover among the 11 basic land cover classes. The dataset is available as 10 m raster.
title: CLCplus Backbone 2018 (raster 10 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides a detailed land cover and land use information for 71 thematic classes for areas along the European coastline for the 2018 reference year. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 0.5 ha and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 10 m and is available as vector data.
title: Coastal Zones Land Cover/Land Use 2018 (vector), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides at pan-European level in the spatial resolution of 20 m the  degree of imperviousness change in the most relevant categories of sealing change (unchanged no sealing, new cover, loss of cover, unchanged sealed, increased sealing, decreased sealing) between the 2015 and 2018 Imperviousness Density status layers.
title: Imperviousness Classified Change 2015-2018 (raster 20 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides detailed land cover and land use information for 55 thematic classes in a variable buffer zone of selected rivers across Europe for the 2018 reference year. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 0.5 ha and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 10 m and is available as vector data.
title: Riparian Zones Land Cover/Land Use 2018 (vector), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides at pan-European level in the spatial resolution of 10 m and 100 m the sealing density in the range from 0% to 100% for the 2018 reference year.
title: Imperviousness Density 2018 (raster 10 m and 100 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides information on land cover and land use changes for 55 thematic classes in selected Natura2000 sites between the 2012 and 2018 reference years. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 0.5 ha and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 10 m and is available as vector data.
title: N2K Land Cover/Land Use Change 2012-2018 (vector), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides a detailed land cover and land use change information for 71 thematic classes for areas along the European coastline between the 2012 and 2018 reference years. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 0.5 ha and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 10 m and is available as vector data.
title: Coastal Zones Land Cover/Land Use Change 2012-2018 (vector), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides information on land cover and land use changes for 55 thematic classes in a variable buffer zone of selected rivers across Europe between the 2012 and 2018 reference years. The dataset has a Minimum Mapping Unit (MMU) of 0.5 ha and a Minimum Mapping Width (MMW) of 10 m and is available as vector data.
title: Riparian Zones Land Cover/Land Use Change 2012-2018 (vector), Europe, 6-yearly

description: Provides at pan-European level in the spatial resolution of 10 m binary information (building / no building) within the sealing outline derived from the Imperviousness Density 2018 including the aggregated Share of Built-up layer in the spatial resolution of 100 m showing the percentage of built-up areas across Europe.
title: Impervious Built-Up 2018 (raster 10 m and 100 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides at pan-European level in the spatial resolution of 20 m and 100 m the degree of imperviousness change (-100% -- +100%) between the 2015 and 2018 Imperviousness Density status layers.
title: Imperviousness Density Change 2015-2018 (raster 20 m and 100 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides at pan-European level in the spatial resolution of 20 m and 100 m the degree of imperviousness change (-100% -- +100%) for the period 2006-2012 and fully aligned with the CORINE Land Cover update cycle.
title: Imperviousness Density Change 2006-2012 (raster 20 m and 100 m), Europe

description: Provides a pan-European spatially consistent and seamless, detailed land cover inventory for the 2021 reference year, for each pixel showing the dominant land cover among the 11 basic land cover classes. The dataset is available as 10 m raster.
title: CLCplus Backbone 2021 (raster 10 m), Europe, 3-yearly

description: Provides a pan-European spatially consistent and seamless, detailed land cover inventory for the 2023 reference year, for each pixel showing the dominant land cover among the 11 basic land cover classes. The dataset is available as 10 m raster.
title: CLCplus Backbone 2023 (raster 10 m), Europe, 2-yearly

title: Herbaceous cover 2023 (raster 10 m), Europe, yearly
